build obj/jpeg_encode.stamp: stamp obj/src/encode/jpeg_encode.SkJPEGWriteUtility.obj obj/src/encode/jpeg_encode.SkJpegEncoderImpl.obj || ./libjpeg.lib ./libjpeg12.lib obj/third_party/libjpeg-turbo/libjpeg_headers.stamp ./libjpeg16.lib
